	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 15"><snpcAnim id="TkkEh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，<delay20 />對了對了！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在這個世界，<delay frames="40" />比起一個人生活，<delay20 />
